					"value": "CTY_Main_A, LOW, teleport to S_LOW_BasiliskGate_FlorrickHangedSpot_343dfb1c-7175-42c6-bca7-dc53cc46c617, set flag LOW_BasiliskGate_State_FlorrickExecutionKnown_aff10649-cfc1-b6d0-0984-5572383cda0a, longrest several times (currently 5x) unitl Florrick gets executed. This guard is spawned on the gallows. Talk to them.\r\n"
